text: Nikolayevka () is a rural locality (a selo) in Ivanovo-Nikolayvsky Selsoviet of Yenotayevsky District, Astrakhan Oblast, Russia. The population was 418 as of 2010. There are 5 streets. == References == Category:Rural localities in Yenotayevsky District
title: Nikolayevka, Yenotayevsky District, Astrakhan Oblast
